1126
01:05:26,380 --> 01:05:28,260
about what is a particle?

1127
01:05:29,260 --> 01:05:30,780
All kind of views.

1128
01:05:32,020 --> 01:05:34,700
Basically, we know some things about it,

1129
01:05:34,700 --> 01:05:37,660
