1130
01:05:37,660 --> 01:05:39,700
Okay, so you go on to the next step.

1131
01:05:42,060 --> 01:05:45,100
I don't think these are questions that can have answers.

1132
01:05:45,100 --> 01:05:46,980
They have answers, but only answers

1133
01:05:46,980 --> 01:05:50,660
